@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_fxcdmr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos(wp.exp(wp.abs(v0 + 0.71)))
    v0 = (v2 * wp.abs(wp.sin(tmp + 0.71)))
    v2 = ((v0 * (v0 + 0.08 + v2 + 0.62)) / wp.cos((v2 + 0.57 / v1 + 0.68)))
    v2 = wp.cos((wp.cos(tmp + 0.31) * tmp))
    v1 = v2
    v1 = (wp.exp(wp.sin(v0 + 0.10)) + (wp.abs(tmp + 0.60) + (tmp + 0.35 - v2 + 0.62)))
    v2 = (0.72 / wp.cos(wp.abs(v2 + 0.10)))
    data[tid] = v0
